Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说会送到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者寄出的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死神送来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着“有您的邮件  请盖章”之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啦  据说是个女孩子送过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这里是再开发区域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是附近有人  务必向他们打听下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  人类  真是麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么活着时不说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有只有死后才说得出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  翔太的字写的还真烂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如这个  怎么读呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是su啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以发明新文字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  小心点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我重要的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  虽说让火箭升空很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是多练练字比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真严格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会会长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  会长本来就是遭人怨恨的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你很能说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时说得多的都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫  绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  早就想说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对绫濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的  我是绫濑明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  妹妹那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  知道了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸…被找到的时候已经是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}海鸥市警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫  绫  绫濑  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察局的人说会送我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现的遗体是住在三上镇的无业者绫濑竹藏先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,45岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}海鸥市  发现男性尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑先生是8号失踪的  家人向警方提出过搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  0913
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这可不是我的错  真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  还有一个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚确实有两个声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来送信的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是绫濑明日奈的恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋  恋人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和绫濑在不同的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是在不同的学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在这栋大楼里相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始第一轮喷射测试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5  4  3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验失败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  绫濑变得经常来看火箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔～  邂逅吗  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  每次我都很头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为怎么解释她都弄不清火箭的构造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  单相思么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这么直接说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信…如果是绫濑明日奈的恋人会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是绫濑竹藏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹…绫濑的爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗言？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从死后的世界寄来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  称为死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者最后留下的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  死者怎么会写信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有身体  巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体的话  当然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后的世界也分等级的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到 level 4 为止  都有身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以写字  还可以吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杖…在说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才开始就在说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅能说话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  站起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是站着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他说你是‘巫女’
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你违反了业务规定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就不能遵守规定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不过是个备置品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把人家当物品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是单纯的杖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在变成人的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}难道真的是杖在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑明日奈没有恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信地址不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有收信人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信  由我接收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶　我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有听见我们说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信人是绫濑明日奈的恋人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是这样合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  那封信没寄到人手上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不去接收绫濑父亲想传达的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来成为她的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你们就无话可说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不错  你还真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛  不错嘛  男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爱  是青春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  真是青涩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心地放进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再用胶带封好  记得写上名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你那边…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘深表遗憾’吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说像大人一样说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  没联络你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙着办市政府那边的手续什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的　那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边才辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦  意外的轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我还很坚强的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑  要是我有什么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个还是让姐姐来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  下次再说可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点忙乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我有重要的话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…虽然这种时候有点不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  喜  喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢  欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭马上就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道你很忙  但要不要来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会等你来了再发射的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  要升空了啊　火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么要是火箭完成了发短信给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么挂掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉碎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}意指翔太告白后被拒绝  然后自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说这种不吉利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事  时机是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  听好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓人的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不面对面跟对方说是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子  也不喜欢在电话里被告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  你打算在火箭升空的那一刻告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那种火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  要是发射失败了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很尴尬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  火箭发射和告白一起缓缓进行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啪地一声爆炸也挺华丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好嘛  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭又不是焰火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成功升空的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送成给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到卫星轨道上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的感情也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  觉得自己刚才那句话很帅？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个一起达成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  是杖就别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是杖  是卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音局  第92点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  话说你们在别人的地盘上放一堆烟出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}看来这份工作得延长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种废品蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}发誓 一定成功发射！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦　谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得取个名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点做过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  她说过他妹妹叫美红
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自言自语些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 卡娜卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杖还要睡觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暂停活动而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说她像人类那样在睡觉的话  她会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶　真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于死后文  你为什么相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人不会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也没被人信任过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是“高中生是不可能成功发射火箭的”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑却相信了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说“好厉害”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“想看升空的那一刻”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我想也试着去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过单纯才美好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家是在明天是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知过别人了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校联络过了　我没什么亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到…还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要到明天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白之时～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是文伽让他想告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想看到死后文送达不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我职业责任感强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和卡娜卡不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  不是还有在用的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探险终于有收效了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等、等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多探险下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太也需要独处的时间嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把信放在翔太那了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音局的指示…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太  你已经看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  什么啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是问你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶作剧也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑…怎么会杀掉自己父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着杀死自己的是女儿明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  还特意要女儿的恋人告发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死  会让人变得坦诚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔也好  怨恨也好  所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从死后的世界寄来的信？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你的我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:18:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么　明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bye bye  美红
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能找到我家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你告诉过我地址
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到你妹妹呢  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  只剩我们两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家没有妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和市政局的人商量过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们进福利机构了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不上高中了  要去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就考虑过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么大学啦梦想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望妹妹有想做的事情时因为没钱而不得不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太也是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力做自己喜欢的事不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  绫濑不可能是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑  火箭完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶　好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢 翔太
